              First off, thanks for taking the time to read this! I'm sure you're busy so I'll keep it short.
            </h1>
            <p data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-duration="700">
              Most of my growing years were spent in Santa Fe, and if you're homeschooled in Santa Fe, you learn how
              to make your own fun. So I started event planning, selling vintage at flea markets, video editing, and
              becoming an expert Youtube learner. From these experiences I learned principles of business, management,
              marketing, and self-starting.
            </p>
            <p data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-duration="700">
